  "slug": "restoring-wales-waters",
  "title": "Restoring Wales' Waters - Cross Party Group",
  "purpose": "To support the recovery and restoration of Wales's rivers, lakes, wetlands and coastal waters, promoting policies and partnerships that improve water quality, ecological health and public enjoyment of the water environment. The Cross-Party Group exists to promote understanding of the condition, management and future of Wales's rivers, lakes, wetlands, estuaries and coastal waters. The Group will provide a forum for Members of the Senedd, stakeholders, communities, regulators, researchers, water companies, environmental organisations, land managers and other interested parties to discuss issues affecting water quality, aquatic ecosystems and the sustainable use of Wales's water environment.",
